definitions.definition: Of or relating to the Umayyad dynasty , which ruled the Umayyad Caliphate from Damascus between 661 and 744 then from Harran until 750, and al-Andalus between 756 and 1031.

main_definition: Of or relating to the Umayyad dynasty , which ruled the Umayyad Caliphate from Damascus between 661 and 744 then from Harran until 750, and al-Andalus between 756 and 1031.
